<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber, Windsheim, Schweinfurt und Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Botschaft kommenden Freitag nach Nürnberg in einer dringlichen Angelegenheit, die nicht schriftlich mitgeteilt werden kann.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="58r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_119_r1l1"><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> Sweinfurt vnd <expan>weiſʒemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_119_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / VVir biten <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Erſame freuntſchaft ernſtlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l3">mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ Jr ewr freunde vnd erber bot </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l4">ſchaft her cʒu vns ſchicken wöllet / daʒ die auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l5">nehſtkunftigen freẏtag cʒu naht hıe beẏ vns ſein / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l6"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etvvaʒ nötlıcher vnd <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache mit Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l9">cʒu reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von ſölcher 
<add><ab facs="#facs_119_line_1574937142579_758">fremder </ab></add> leuffe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> als <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l10"><expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein die vns niht füglich ſein cʒu <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l11">ſeit darynne niht ſewmig / das wöllen etc / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l12">das den von <expan>winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>weiſʒe<ex>n</ex>b<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd Sweinfürt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r1l14">auch alſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Dẏoniſij A vııȷ<hi rend="sup">uo</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="58r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
                        Sweinfurt und <expan>Weiszemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir biten <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ersame freuntschaft ernstlich mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz,
                        daz ir ewr freunde und erber bot schaft her czu uns schicken wöllet, daz die
                        auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">nehstkunftigen freytag</q> 12.10.1408</note>
</app> czu naht hie bey uns sein, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etwaz
                        nötlicher und <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache mit in czu reden
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von sölcher <add>fremder</add> leuffe
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        in <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, die uns niht füglich sein czu
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und seit darynne niht sewmig. Das
                        wöllen etc. <expan>Wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das den von
                                <expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>Weisze<ex>n</ex>b<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und Sweinfürt auch also
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Dyonisii a
                            viii<hi rend="sup">vo</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
